{
  "texts": [
    "The study discovered that using more than two features simultaneously had some impact on the results of student-grade prediction.",
    "The proposed feature combination approach can automatically learn feature combinations, consider the influence of first-order, second-order, and highorder features, and gather relationship data between each feature and performance.",
    "The experimental results showed that the proposed method achieved an accuracy of approximately 86.6%.",
    "A study by Rahman et al (2022) suggested a strategy for gathering institutional data, analyzing and preprocessing the data, and using DNNs to estimate student's progress and the final CGPA.",
    "To analyze the prediction of student quality, a realtime dataset was created from student transcript data from a reputable university in Bangladesh."
  ]
}